April 25, 1965 D Cottingham Entertainment Contest
Cottingham Entertainment Contest 0 Entertainments Contest
cottingham-entertainment-contest
None
Cottingham Secondary School, East Yorkshire Contest was by invitation only to bands local to Cottingham. Hull City Police were a Military Band but were allowed to enter.
5 bands competed.
Audience appeal adjudicator: Mrs V. A. Jarvis, Cottingham Staging adjudicator: J. Mackenzie Green, entertainment manager, Hornsea
Presentations were made to Mr Leonard Fallowfield and Mr Harry A. Robb, for over 40 years service to brass bands.
Most Overall Marks: Hull City Police Best Hymn: Hull City Police
